---
source: crates/loom/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: "loom_help(&[\"note\"])"
---
Manage notes for a spec

Usage: loom note [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  set    Replace all notes for the spec
  add    Append a single note to the spec
  clear  Delete notes for the spec
  list   List notes for the spec
  rm     Remove a single note by id
  help   Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -w, --workspace <PATH>  Workspace root. Defaults to the current working directory
  -A, --agent <BACKEND>   Override the agent backend for this invocation [possible values: claude, pi]
  -h, --help              Print help
